## 三、接口预留方案（暂不上线）

### 3.1 短信通知接口

**设计原则**：界面和流程完整实现，仅发送功能做模拟

```typescript
// 接口预留实现示例
interface SMSService {
  sendVerificationCode(phone: string): Promise<{success: boolean, message: string}>;
  sendOrderNotification(orderId: string, template: string): Promise<{success: boolean}>;
  sendAppointmentReminder(appointmentId: string): Promise<{success: boolean}>;
}

// 预留接口实现（控制台日志模拟）
export const mockSMSService: SMSService = {
  sendVerificationCode: async (phone) => {
    console.log(`[MOCK SMS] 发送验证码到 ${phone}: 您的验证码是 123456`);
    return { success: true, message: '短信接口已预留，验证码: 123456' };
  },
  sendOrderNotification: async (orderId, template) => {
    console.log(`[MOCK SMS] 订单 ${orderId} 发送通知: ${template}`);
    return { success: true };
  },
  sendAppointmentReminder: async (appointmentId) => {
    console.log(`[MOCK SMS] 预约 ${appointmentId} 发送提醒`);
    return { success: true };
  }
};
```

**UI表现**：
- 发送按钮正常显示
- 点击后弹出提示："短信接口已预留（模拟发送成功）"
- 控制台输出模拟日志

