## 六、数据库表结构设计

### 6.1 核心表清单

| 表名 | 说明 | 关键字段 |
|------|------|----------|
| users | 用户表 | id, email, role, department, is_outsource |
| orders | 订单表 | id, user_id, status, created_by, appointment_id |
| order_logs | 订单日志 | id, order_id, action, operator_id, from_status, to_status |
| documents | 资料文档 | id, order_id, type, file_url, uploaded_by, status |
| appointments | 预约信息 | id, order_id, appointment_date, document_url, status |
| messages | 站内消息(预留) | id, from_user, to_user, content, read_at |

### 6.2 订单状态流转表

```sql
-- 订单状态流转规则表
CREATE TABLE order_transitions (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  from_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  to_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  allowed_roles VARCHAR(255)[] NOT NULL,  -- 允许执行该操作的角色
  action_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,        -- 操作名称
  action_label VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,       -- 显示名称
  requires_document BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,   -- 是否需要上传资料
  notification_template VARCHAR(50),          -- 发送通知模板
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- 初始化9大状态流转规则
INSERT INTO order_transitions (from_status, to_status, allowed_roles, action_name, action_label) VALUES
('pending_connect', 'connected', ARRAY['customer_service'], 'accept_order', '接单'),
('connected', 'collecting', ARRAY['clerk'], 'start_collect', '开始收集资料'),
('collecting', 'pending_review', ARRAY['clerk'], 'submit_review', '提交审核'),
('pending_review', 'reviewing', ARRAY['operator'], 'accept_review', '接受审核'),
('reviewing', 'processing', ARRAY['operator'], 'start_processing', '开始制作'),
('processing', 'pending_delivery', ARRAY['operator'], 'ready_delivery', '待交付'),
('pending_delivery', 'delivered', ARRAY['clerk'], 'confirm_delivery', '确认交付'),
('delivered', 'approved', ARRAY['clerk', 'operator'], 'approve', '出签'),
('delivered', 'rejected', ARRAY['clerk', 'operator'], 'reject', '拒签');
```

